<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢ - <span class="c2">(١١٩٠)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">وَابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1580">الْحَكَمِ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>يُحَدِّثُ، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">الْأَسْوَدِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> أَنَّهَا قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">« كَأَنَّمَا أَنْظُرُ إِلَى وَبِيصِ الطِّيبِ فِي مَفَارِقِ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَهُوَ مُحْرِمٌ »</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>